message.entry: Radius and Dimensions properties must not be specified together.
Radius property must not be used with "{0}" arrangement. Use Dimensions property with "{0}" arrangement.
Dimensions property must not be used with "{0}" arrangement. Use Radius property with "{0}" arrangement.
Arrangement "{0}" is for encoding two-dimensional environment. Use "{1}" or "{2}" arrangement.
Arrangement "{0}" is for encoding three-dimensional environment. Use "{1}" or "{2}" arrangement.
